        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（天使捧旨上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "天使",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "旨意下，跪。姬昌听读。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "天使",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣上赐下酒肉馒首，命卿家食用。用了馒首，封为西岐文王；若待不用，定斩"
        },
        {
          "character": "天使",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不饶。旨意读罢，三呼望诏谢恩！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知大人捧旨到来，失误远迎，多多有罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "天使",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好说。圣上赐来酒肉馒首，就该用了，老夫好去交旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一奸妃，明明是我儿的首级剁为肉泥，包成馒首，若待不用，定斩不饶。也"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢！暂记腹内，逃出朝歌再做区处。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人待我拜谢皇恩，食用馒首，也就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姬昌吃。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "天使",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（天使下。姬昌下。）"
        }
